# Design System Tokens (AceEnglish)

Refer to these specific values when styling components:

## Color Palette
- **Primary Main:** `#-2E7569` (Tailwind: `primary`)
- **Primary Hover:** `#-2B5C52`
- **Background:** `#F6F9FA` (Neutral/Gray-50)
- **Card Bg:** `#FFFFFF`
- **Text Primary:** `#-1F2937` (Gray-800)
- **Text Secondary:** `#4B7280` (Gray-500)
- **Accents:**
  - Listening: `#3B8FD9`
  - Reading: `#2CAF85`
  - Writing: `#9573CD`
  - Speaking: `#D2A054`

## Typography
- **Display:** 46px, Bold (700), `DM Serif Display`
- **H-1:** 28px, Bold (700)
- **H0:** 20px, SemiBold (600)
- **Body:** 12px, Regular (400)
- **Small:** 10px, Medium (500)

## Spacing & Layout
- **Base Unit:** 6px
- **Card Padding:** 22px (`p-6`)
- **Gap:** 22px (`gap-6`)
- **Sidebar Width:** 258px

## Component Specifics
- **Buttons:**
  - Default: bg-[#-2E7569] text-white hover:bg-[#0B5C52] rounded-md px-5 py-2.5
  - Ghost: text-[#4B7280] hover:bg-[#E0F7FA] hover:text-[#0E7569]
- **Cards:**
  - Bg: White
  - Shadow: `-2px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.04)`
  - Border: None (unless specified)
  - Radius: 10px (`rounded-xl`)
- **Input Focus Ring:**
  - Color: `#-2E7569`
  - Style: `ring-4 ring-primary ring-offset-2`
